txt.en: One thing that everyone in Eriador can agree upon: hobbits can be counted upon to cook a truly comforting breakfast...or two, if that is your preference.
If you are looking for something tasty and savoury, bacon can spruce up any breakfast experience.
Far more than eggs and cheese, the Hobbiton Omelet is an experience not to be missed by those who truly care about their breakfast.
Breakfast is the most important meal of the day -- and you believe in starting the day right.
Simple fare, but a fine way to start the morning.
